OL,3,CDatshiane Navanayagam investigates the
OL,4,Csteps can we take to beat fatigue.
OL,6,FAccording to one 2022 survey more than
OL,7,Fa third of us feel tired most or all
OL,8,Fof the time. In this week's episode of
OL,9,FTONIGHT reporter Datshiane Navanayagam
OL,10,Fhas been finding out why we are so
OL,11,Ftired and what we can do to beat it.
OL,13,FDatshiane looks at her own tiredness
OL,14,Flevels for the programme, after
OL,15,Fexperiencing fatigue herself for some
OL,16,Ftime. She meets sleep expert Joshua
OL,17,FPiper who gives her advice:
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
