OL,3,CDatshiane Navanayagam investigates the
OL,4,Csteps can we take to beat fatigue.
OL,6,F"I think it's important to have a
OL,7,Ffixed wake-up time and get good
OL,8,Fexposure to sunlight ideally, but you
OL,9,Fcan also use things like daylight
OL,10,Flamps these days. Having that behavior
OL,11,Fon a regular basis, your brain's very
OL,12,Fgood at patterns. It starts to learn
OL,13,Fthis is wake up time" - JOSHUA PIPER,
OL,14,FSleep clinician, Resmed
OL,16,FDatshiane also seeks advice from Dr
OL,17,FAlison Grimston, an expert in women's
OL,18,Fhealth, who says:
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@UO]
