OL,3,CDatshiane Navanayagam investigates the
OL,4,Csteps can we take to beat fatigue.
OL,6,F"I see it every day in practice as a
OL,7,Fclinician. And it's particularly
OL,8,Fcommon in people who are stressed in
OL,9,Ftheir jobs, people who aren't sleeping
OL,10,Fproperly, and women in perimenopause".
OL,11,F- DR ALISON GRIMSTON, Dr Finlay's
OL,12,FPrivate Practice
OL,14,FDr Alison runs some tests, to see if
OL,15,Fthere are any medical reasons
OL,16,Fcontributing to Datshiane's tiredness,
OL,17,Fwe find out her results later on in
OL,18,Fthe programme.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
