OL,3,CDatshiane Navanayagam investigates the
OL,4,Csteps can we take to beat fatigue.
OL,6,FIn Greater Manchester 38 year old
OL,7,FLaura has been experiencing the
OL,8,Fstrains of fatigue, she cares for her
OL,9,Felderly relative whilst also holding
OL,10,Fdown a full time job:
OL,12,F"As a carer I'm just permanently
OL,13,Ftired. I don't remember a time when I
OL,14,Fwasn't. I wake up tired and by the end
OL,15,Fof the day I am absolutely exhausted.
OL,16,FEverything just sort of is, just more
OL,17,Fdifficult when you're tired." - LAURA
OL,26,@tD@AOUyD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
