OL,3,CDatshiane Navanayagam investigates the
OL,4,Csteps can we take to beat fatigue.
OL,6,FWe pair Laura up with expert in
OL,7,Fnutrition Faye Thompson, and Ruth
OL,8,FRosselson, a mindfulness teacher, who
OL,9,Foffer her some advice to see if some
OL,10,Fsmall changes could make a difference.
OL,12,F"She's not valuing food as well as she
OL,13,Fcould do. It's going to be about
OL,14,Fmaking her understand what types of
OL,15,Ffood she needs to be eating and when
OL,16,Fshe needs to be eating them"- FAYE
OL,17,FTHOMPSON, Lift Nutrition & Wellness
OL,19,FAnd Ruth advises:
OL,26,@tD@AOUxD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
