OL,3,CDatshiane Navanayagam investigates the
OL,4,Csteps can we take to beat fatigue.
OL,6,F"I'm also gonna suggest a little short
OL,7,Fmeditation before bed to help her
OL,8,Fswitch off, and I hope that over time
OL,9,Fshe'll be able to enjoy the downtime
OL,10,Fthat she does have without worrying
OL,11,Fabout all the things that she has to
OL,12,Fdo". - RUTH ROSSELSON, Manchester Mind
OL,14,FUnpaid carers like Laura can
OL,15,Fexperience high levels of burn out,
OL,16,Fwith one report putting it as high as
OL,17,F77%, but it's something that can creep
OL,18,Fup on any of us.
OL,20,FDr Claire Ashley is a specialist in
OL,21,Fburnout, she says:
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@CO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
