OL,3,CDatshiane Navanayagam investigates the
OL,4,Csteps can we take to beat fatigue.
OL,6,F"Burnout does have some pretty serious
OL,7,Fconsequences for your physical health
OL,8,Fas well as your mental and emotional
OL,9,Fhealth, but the good news is that with
OL,10,Frecovery that these risks can go back
OL,11,Fto your normal baseline". DR CLAIRE
OL,12,FASHLEY, GP & Burnout Specialist
OL,14,FIf you're experiencing tiredness then
OL,15,Fit could be that you're deficient in
OL,16,Firon. According to one study, across
OL,17,Fthe UK around 17% of the population is
OL,18,Firon deficient, and that figure
OL,19,Fincreases for women as they enter
OL,20,Fadulthood and beyond.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
