OL,3,CDatshiane Navanayagam investigates the
OL,4,Csteps can we take to beat fatigue.
OL,6,FTONIGHT visits a Pilates class in Bury
OL,7,Fto see what they know about iron
OL,8,Fdeficiencies and the link to being
OL,9,Ftired. The class all agreed to do a
OL,10,Fsimple finger prick test to check
OL,11,Ftheir iron levels and once the results
OL,12,Fwere gathered, there was a surprise in
OL,13,Fstore for the majority of the class.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
