PN,30709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775761868
OL,3,CDatshiane Navanayagam investigates the
OL,4,Csteps can we take to beat fatigue.
OL,6,FAnd as for Datshiane? Well she also
OL,7,Freceives her test results back from Dr
OL,8,FAlison. They show she has borderline
OL,9,Flow iron, a slightly low folate level
OL,10,Fand a significant vitamin D
OL,11,Fdeficiency, which she is going to look
OL,12,Fto address with diet changes,
OL,13,Fsupplements and increasing her
OL,14,Fexposure to sunlight.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
