OL,3,CDatshiane Navanayagam investigates the
OL,4,Csteps can we take to beat fatigue.
OL,6,FIf you find that tiredness has taken
OL,7,Fcontrol, advice from the experts in
OL,8,Fthe programme is a definite starting
OL,9,Fpoint; try taking a look at your sleep
OL,10,Fpatterns and your use of technology,
OL,11,Ffind time for your mind, and check
OL,12,Fyou're getting all the nutrients that
OL,13,Fyour body needs. And if all else
OL,14,Ffails, seek medical advice.
OL,16,FUSEFUL LINKS:
OL,18,FMENTAL HEALTH FOUNDATION - Burnout:
OL,19,Fsigns, causes and ways to recover
